{"tid":1638834,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"應承我好唔好","createTime":"2019-10-08T12:20:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T13:14:58.000Z","uid":188828,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1002499253befcfa403b91c661b9b58be4c5c55f","tid":1638834,"uid":188828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T12:20:37.000Z","msg":"自從出實彈同蒙面法之後<br />\n我知大家心情都愈來愈不安<br />\n好似睇唔見出路甚至每日都懷疑自己做既野有冇用<br />\n我想同大家講幾句<br />\n<br />\n我地企出黎唔係收咗錢、唔係貪玩<br />\n係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">因為我地做緊自己認為正確既事</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好因為賽後檢討而傷感情<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">有時手足粗聲粗氣係因為當你係一家人</span><br />\n我地對最親既家人永遠最直接同冇禮貌<br />\n但記住無論點都好<br />\n我地係一體黎<br />\n<br />\n應承我<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">記住每一句被侮辱既說話<br />\n記住每一單性侵<br />\n記住每一下警棍<br />\n記住每一粒催淚彈<br />\n記住每一粒海綿彈<br />\n記住每一粒橡膠子彈<br />\n記住每一粒實彈<br />\n記住每一位逝去既義士<br />\n記住每一位失蹤既手足<br />\n記住流過既每一滴血<br />\n記住流過既每一滴眼淚</span><br />\n<br />\n應承我<br />\n永遠都不割<br />\n永遠都唔好原諒班仆街<br />\n好唔好<br />\n<br />\n我唔知場運動會持續幾耐<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">但只要仲有一個人出黎<br />\n我都仍然會企出黎</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n天佑香港<br />\n願榮光歸香港"},{"pid":"34187e7743681537475e5eb472cf12b3d81069db","tid":1638834,"uid":188828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T12:21:57.000Z","msg":"塞車路上諗好多野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89bbc2e7ecc2907f8d78f05a25122a90b5985cf9","tid":1638834,"uid":188828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T12:22:40.000Z","msg":"唔好放棄<br />\n唔好再成日話輸！！！"},{"pid":"d7c1cd07e4d3ccd1a5b16d2ed7c33f205c3905b2","tid":1638834,"uid":188828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T12:23:03.000Z","msg":"唔好絕望！！！"},{"pid":"c4640e67cc840ce670345439511c4daeca6d3593","tid":1638834,"uid":188828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T12:23:22.000Z","msg":"吹水台應該都冇咩人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c6c3b1cc69df5135d99fcdb4d2dd088b2c0495d","tid":1638834,"uid":108764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T13:07:57.000Z","msg":"Assassin's Creed 3 HK篇《香港人：反抗》<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1628253\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1628253</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\nOk應承你"},{"pid":"9820cbb31610bf957b73e23f77c6b802ac4bde12","tid":1638834,"uid":51142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T13:14:58.000Z","msg":"繼續堅持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家同行"}]}